Butteville Curbside Meals -
We will be providing curbside meal pickup for anyone that wants a meal. Please contact Colton Cheffey at colton.cheffey@butteville.k12.ca.us or call the kitchen at (530) 938-9753 if you want to come to the school and pickup a hot meal and breakfast. There will be three pickup times for hot school lunches. The times are 10:40-11am, 11:10-11:30am, and 11:40am-12pm. When you pick up your lunch, we will provide you with breakfast for the next morning. Monday’s breakfast will be served when you pick up your Friday meal.
